      "note": "description",
      "abstract": "Requires the Hawaii State Energy Office to implement and administer a three-year phased Water-Energy Resilience Competitive Grant Program in the County of Maui.  Requires reports to the Legislature.  Appropriates funds.  Repeals 6/30/2027.  Effective 7/1/2050.  (SD1)"
    }
